headline: AES Announces Quarterly Dividend
summary: The Board of Directors of The AES Corporation (NYSE: AES) declared a quarterly common stock dividend of $0.17595 per share payable on February 13, 2026 to shareholders of record at the close of business on January 30, 2026.
